main.main.header-with-image
  section.main-welcome
    .main-img.pl-4.pt-5
      img.img-fluid(src='/images/logo.png' alt='logo')
    .main-heading
      h1.main-heading_title
        | Welcome to Salva
      p.main-heading_text
        | We are the best student bank as we specifically tailor our features to students enabling them to get the best use from our services
      a.btn.main-heading_button.btn-lg.rounded-lg.mt-4(href="sign_up")
        | Get started
      a.ca3-scroll-down-link.ca3-scroll-down-arrow(data-ca3_iconfont='ETmodules' data-ca3_icon='')
section.bank-services
  .container
    .row
      .service.col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-xs-12
        .card
          .card-img-wrapper
            img.card-img-top(src='/images/main-welcome_img9.jpg' alt='Card image cap')
          .card-body
            h5.card-title Create accounts with 0% interest charged on overdraft
            p.card-text
              | Get started with an interest free overdraft of Â£500 where you can contact us to increase it subject to certain requirements.
            a.btn.btn-primary(href="sign_up") Get started
      .service.col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-xs-12
        .card
          .card-img-wrapper
            img.card-img-top(src='/images/main-welcome_img10.jpg' alt='Card image cap')
          .card-body
            h5.card-title Supported banking
            p.card-text
              | We, as a bank, want to give the necessary financial support to students which may be a factor in an increase in students as they'll have the financial support to attend higher education.
            a.btn.btn-primary(href="sign_up") Get started
      .service.col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-xs-12
        .card
          .card-img-wrapper
            img.card-img-top(src='/images/main-welcome_img11.jpg' alt='Card image cap')
          .card-body
            h5.card-title The bank that makes saving easy
            p.card-text
              | Start saving with our bank with a set interest rate of 2%. This shows the reliability and benefit of our bank as our interest rate will never change and it's set at a high percentage.
            a.btn.btn-primary(href="sign_up") Get started
